SECTION 14: INTEGER TRACEABILITY
----------------------------------------------------------------------

  Every integer used traces to the gauge group:

  11  = Yang-Mills coefficient from Lorentz + gauge + renormalizability
  19  = |numerator(b2_SM * 6)| = |(-19/6) * 6| = 19
  13  = |numerator(b2_mod * 6)| = |(-13/6) * 6| = 13
  20  = |b3_mod * 3| = |(-20/3) * 3| = 20
  22  = 2 * YM = 2 * 11 = 22
  57  = 3 * 19 = N_gen * |b2_SM_num| = 57
  39  = 3 * 13 = N_gen * |b2_mod_num| = 39
  44  = 4 * 11 = 4 * YM = 44
  169 = 13^2 = |b2_mod_num|^2 = 169

